description: This is a market on whether Rafael Nadal will win the Roland-Garros (French Open) in the Men’s Singles category, currently scheduled to take place between May 24, 2021 and June 13, 2021. The market will resolve to “Yes” if Rafael Nadal wins the Roland-Garros and “No” otherwise. If the tournament is postponed to an end date on or before July 1, 2021, the same market conditions will apply. If the tournament does not end until after July 1, 2021, or is cancelled altogether, the market will resolve to 50-50. In the event of ambiguity in terms of the market outcome, the market will be resolved in good faith at the sole discretion of the Markets Integrity Committee (MIC).
